mqtt-grafana
============

Read-only SQLite-to-JSON CGI endpoint for the Freetz web server on port 81.

Installed URL:
  http://fritz.box:81/cgi-bin/mqtt-grafana.cgi

Parameters:
  from=UNIX_SECONDS       default: now - 3600
  to=UNIX_SECONDS         default: now
  topic=MQTT_TOPIC        optional exact match
  limit=ROWS              default: 2000, capped by menuconfig value
  mode=health             database health/latest timestamp response

Example:
  /cgi-bin/mqtt-grafana.cgi?topic=sensor/temp&from=1700000000&to=1700003600

The endpoint returns timestamps in milliseconds for Grafana and preserves the
original payload. A numeric value field is set when the complete payload is a
valid finite number.

Build note for version 1.0.1:
The CGI links libm after libsqlite3 because numeric MQTT payload handling uses
floating-point classification functions such as isfinite().
